---
// ProblemSection - Pain points highlighting gym owner challenges
---

<section class="problem-section" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <!-- Pain Points Grid -->
      <div class="pain-points">
        <div class="pain-point card-cream">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="22 17 13.5 8.5 8.5 13.5 2 7"/>
              <polyline points="16 17 22 17 22 11"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>The Lead Drought</h3>
          <p>Running ads that generate 'leads' but nobody ever answers the phone or walks in.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pain-point card-dark">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Member Churn</h3>
          <p>Losing members as fast as you sign them up, keeping you stuck on a treadmill.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pain-point card-cream offset-up">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Owner Burnout</h3>
          <p>Spending 14 hours a day in the gym instead of working on the vision.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pain-point card-cream">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Thin Margins</h3>
          <p>Operating at a scale that barely covers the overhead and payroll each month.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Does your gym feel like a <span class="highlight">leaky bucket?</span></h2>
        <p class="description">
          Most gym owners try to solve their problems with "more ads." But without a system to convert those leads and retain them long-term, you're just throwing money down the drain.
        </p>
        <ul class="benefits">
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            <span>Stop relying on word-of-mouth hope marketing.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            <span>Eliminate the "ghosting" from low-quality leads.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            <span>Turn your facility into a predictable profit machine.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#booking" class="cta-link">
          Let's fix it together
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .problem-section {
      padding: 8rem 0;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
    }
  }

  /* Pain Points Grid */
  .pain-points {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    order: 2;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pain-points {
      order: 1;
    }
  }

  .pain-point {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .card-cream {
    background: hsl(var(--cream));
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--forest) / 0.05);
  }

  .card-dark {
    background: hsl(var(--forest));
    color: white;
  }

  .offset-up {
    margin-top: -2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .offset-up {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  }

  .icon {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-cream .icon {
    color: hsl(var(--forest));
  }

  .card-dark .icon {
    color: hsl(var(--cream));
  }

  .pain-point h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pain-point p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .card-cream p {
    color: hsl(var(--forest) / 0.7);
  }

  .card-dark p {
    color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.7);
  }

  /* Content */
  .content {
    order: 1;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .content {
      order: 2;
    }
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: hsl(var(--gold));
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .benefits {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .benefits li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .benefits svg {
    color: hsl(var(--gold));
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  .cta-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: hsl(var(--forest));
    border-bottom: 2px solid hsl(var(--forest));
    padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-link:hover {
    color: hsl(var(--gold));
    border-color: hsl(var(--gold));
  }

  .cta-link svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-link:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
